---
title: Activity Diagram - Check-in Tamu
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Tamu Tiba di Hotel]) --> Greet[Front Desk Sambut Tamu]
    Greet --> AskRef[Minta Booking Reference / Nama]
    AskRef --> Search[Cari di /occupancy]
    Search --> Found{Reservasi<br/>Ditemukan?}
    Found -->|Tidak| WalkIn{Walk-in?}
    WalkIn -->|Ya| CreateRes[Buat Reservasi Baru]
    CreateRes --> VerifyData
    WalkIn -->|Tidak| EndErr([Maaf, tidak ada reservasi])
    Found -->|Ya| VerifyData[Verifikasi Identitas + KTP]
    VerifyData --> ValidID{ID Valid?}
    ValidID -->|Tidak| EndErr2([Tolak Check-in])
    ValidID -->|Ya| CekDeposit{Bayar<br/>Deposit?}
    CekDeposit -->|Belum| Deposit[Catat Deposit]
    Deposit --> UpdateStatus
    CekDeposit -->|Sudah| UpdateStatus[UPDATE reservation status='checked-in']
    UpdateStatus --> UpdateRoom[UPDATE room status='occupied']
    UpdateRoom --> Charge[INSERT billing_items: Room Charge]
    Charge --> KeyCard[Berikan Kartu Kunci]
    KeyCard --> Notif[Notifikasi ke Housekeeping]
    Notif --> End([Tamu Masuk Kamar])

    classDef startEnd fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
    classDef decision fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f57f17,color:#000
    classDef action fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    classDef error fill:#ffcdd2,stroke:#c62828,color:#000
    class Start,End startEnd
    class Found,WalkIn,ValidID,CekDeposit decision
    class Greet,AskRef,Search,CreateRes,VerifyData,Deposit,UpdateStatus,UpdateRoom,Charge,KeyCard,Notif action
    class EndErr,EndErr2 error
